<span id="freeTextContainer7789444148419930317">Very good psychological horror novel. It starts out so bland, you wonder if it&apos;s going to be scary at all. But slowly the tension builds. At the half-way point I was so creeped out by it, I couldn&apos;t read it at night. A house emanating evil, causing worse and worse tragedy to each new family that lives in it. I also liked the book because it doesn&apos;t blatantly show there is a supernatural connection, leaving you to decide for yourself. Subtle, well-written and worth reading.</span>
  <span id="freeText7789444148419930317" style="display:none">Very good psychological horror novel. It starts out so bland, you wonder if it's going to be scary at all. But slowly the tension builds. At the half-way point I was so creeped out by it, I couldn't read it at night. A house emanating evil, causing worse and worse tragedy to each new family that lives in it. I also liked the book because it doesn't blatantly show there is a supernatural connection, leaving you to decide for yourself. Subtle, well-written and worth reading.</span>
