          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Walter loves the sea, and I need it in some elemental way that I cannot even come close to verbalizing. I become dim and shriveled somehow at my very core if I am away from the sea too long. When I return to it I seem to fill up and overflow with it, soaking in the vast, sighing wetness of it like a parched vine in a long, soft spring rain.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
